name: Alexa Bliss - Textual Inversion
description:
This is a textual inversion trained on pictures of wrestler Alexa Bliss aka Alexis Cabrera.

This ti was requested by user @rimale.

I hope you enjoy using this ti as much as I do.

Still learning and improving the progress of the training, any feedback is welcome.

Feel free to leave me a tip/buy me a coffee if you like what I am doing :)
